Our latest soft goods project with @four_horsemen_studios - RED DEATH!
This was both challenging and fun to make. We were tasked to make a multi-layered and assymetrical robe that also features a hood that extends to the floor. The main challenge was to make everything look coherent and ghastly at the same time. This one took a lot of planning since it could easily look really off with all the layers of softgoods. Hope you guys like it!
